Stairway to the Akira-bar~
You find yourself standing in the stairway of a small, quiet 
bar. This is the hangout of a local gang of motorbike punks. A 
small light near the street flickers on and off, as if it's 
bulb isin't properly inserted. Looking down at the door to the 
bar, you notice a small sign that says `6"`^Adults Only`6"``.
