Above the bar~
You stand atop the stairs next to a small apartment. A small 
sign on the wall warns all who aren't the manager to stay out. 
A medium sized wooden door lies to the west, it's doorknob rusty.
Looking closer you notice that the door is cracked. You think 
to yourself `6'`^I'm sure the manager wouldn't mind if I take a`` 
`^look at his fine home`6'``.
